$ Windows Settings: Apps


{ Choose where to get apps

  Specifiy from where apps can be installed. The list includes
    • Anywhere
    • Anywhere, but let me know if there's a comparable app in the Microsoft Store
    • Anywere, but warn me before installing an app that's not from the Microsoft Store
    • The Microsoft Store only (*recommended*)

}
